Notice I clearly labeled it &quot;For me&quot;. I have many friends that work outside the home and do not have this problem. But MY job and MY situation led to it in MY life. So for me, the work was causing stress that I needed to get rid of. So I did. So actually, in a way, I agreed with Stacy that I was less stressed at home, though I know others that aren't.<br>
