<br>
Ok, this is more for the working moms more than for the SAHP, but any input would be good.  Also, if DBC could respond that would be great also, since he is the only guy that I know of that posts here.<br>
<br>
Anyway, I am wandering how the household &quot;chores&quot; are split up in your household with both parents working?  In DBC's case I am wandering how things are now and how would they most likely be if his wife went to work?  And do any of you wives have a problem with your husbands treating your job or time less important?  (I am kind of leaning to if you make less money than your husband, but not excluded to that.)<br>
<br>
